dc_title_s: Map of Ypsilanti, Mich.; drawn from actual surveys & official records by C. S. Woodard.
dc_description_s: Blueline negative copy. Cadastral map showing some land ownership. 1 map on 2 sheets: photocopy.; 114 x 80 cm., sheets 58 x 81 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
